{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore inside the human body  as a COVID-virus. This is the demo of COVID-29, a single player, action-adventure, indie game created by a doctor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The demo includes most of the game's gameplay elements but only the first half of the first level is included. Character customization is not included.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Single player</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Third person</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Punching</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kicking</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shooting magic projectiles</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Item attacks</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Climbing</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492350/extras/Gif_Climbing_616x180.gif?t=1738563061\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Style</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Action-Adventure</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Souls-like elements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Medieval mixed with biology style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Platforming</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Character</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as a  COVID-virus fighting immune cells and immune proteins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492350/extras/Gif_C1_616x180.gif?t=1738563061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Goals</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Work your way through the body and infect as many cells as possible</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect resources to craft items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kill immune cells and immune proteins</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492350/extras/Gif_InfectingCell_616x180.gif?t=1738563061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Enemies encountered in the demo</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">White blood cell warriors (Neutrophils)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spawner drone (B-cells)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wild spiders (C1 immune proteins)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wild worms (Protease protein)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492350/extras/Gif_Neutrophil_616x180.gif?t=1738563061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">White blood cell warriors (Neutrophils)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Items and crafting</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Consumable biology-related items can be crafted from peptide resources collected through the maps by breaking bush-like proteins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Maps</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492350/extras/LevelLungs_2.44.1.png?t=1738563061\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lung airway. The demo includes half of this level.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tutorial level. Helps you learn the basic game mechanics.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gameplay duration of the demo: 30-50 minutes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492350/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738563061","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492350/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738563061","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492350/4d679a8ed435ba1073c20850870508b76b5bec78/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738563061","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492350/4d679a8ed435ba1073c20850870508b76b5bec78/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738563061","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore inside the human body  as a COVID-virus. This is the demo of COVID-29, a single player, action-adventure, indie game created by a doctor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The demo includes most of the game's gameplay elements but only the first half of the first level is included. Character customization is not included.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Single player</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Third person</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Punching</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kicking</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shooting magic projectiles</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Item attacks</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Climbing</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"